prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon-style hippopotamus wearing a tiny, jaunty party hat, trying to gracefully balance on one leg in a clumsy ballet pose. The hippo has a look of cheerful determination on its face. Soft, pastel watercolor splashes of confetti float around it. In the center, the words "happy birthday" are written in a beautiful, readable, flowing handwritten cursive script. The entire design is a flat 2D artwork in a watercolor painting style, featuring soft flowing colors, visible artistic brush strokes, a subtle paper texture, and organic paint bleeds at the edges of the hippo and confetti.
